2017-01-04  Pauli Nieminen  <suokkos@gmail.com>
	    Jonathan Wakely  <jwakely@redhat.com>

	PR libstdc++/64735
	* acinclude.m4 (GLIBCXX_CHECK_EXCEPTION_PTR_SYMVER): Define.
	* config.h.in: Regenerate.
